sequenceDiagram
    participant T as Teste Playwright
    participant B as Navegador
    participant F as Frontend React
    participant API as Backend Express
    participant DB as Banco SQLite

    T->>B: Abre navegador
    T->>B: Navega para /criar
    B->>F: Renderiza formulario
    T->>B: Preenche nome e descricao
    T->>B: Clica em Salvar
    B->>F: Dispara evento submit
    F->>API: POST /api/projects
    API->>DB: INSERT project
    DB-->>API: project created
    API-->>F: 201 + project data
    F-->>B: Redireciona para /projetos/:id
    B-->>T: Pagina carregada
    T->>B: Verifica titulo do projeto
    T->>B: Fecha navegador